#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: timeslot-booking.php widgets/class-tsb-widget.php:19
msgid "Timeslot Booking"
msgstr ""

#. Description of the plugin
#: timeslot-booking.php
msgid ""
"Custom Elementor widget. Predefined timeslots from an hour range, individual "
"blocks removable, auto-blocks weekends + Danish bank holidays, contact form "
"after slot pick, double-booking prevented."
msgstr ""
"Brugerdefineret Elementor-widget. Foruddefinerede tidspunkter fra et "
"timeinterval, enkelte blokeringer kan fjernes, blokerer automatisk weekender "
"+ danske helligdage, kontaktformular efter valg af tid, dobbeltbooking "
"forhindret."

